<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id6c891faa-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2020—<ref href="/us/pl/116/271">Pub. L. 116–271</ref> amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section related to authorization of appropriations for fiscal years 2009 to 2013.</p>
